Sentencas: We report the design and fabrication of a novel electrode-supported honeycomb solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC), that can generate high volumetric power density.
Titulo: Design and Fabrication of a Novel Electrode-Supported Honeycomb SOFC

Sentencas: Among various cell designs, honeycomb SOFCs are suitable for compact SOFC modules because they have a large surface electrode area per unit volume.
Titulo: Design and Fabrication of a Novel Electrode-Supported Honeycomb SOFC

Sentencas: We have succeeded in fabricating a cathode-supported honeycomb SOFC via extrusion of a LaSrMnO(3) honeycomb monolith and through the use of a new slurry injection method for the channel surface coating using electrolyte/anode bi-layers.
Titulo: Design and Fabrication of a Novel Electrode-Supported Honeycomb SOFC

Sentencas: The fabricated honeycomb SOFCs exhibited high volumetric power densities of approximately 1.2 W/cm(3) at 600 degrees C under a wet H(2) fuel flow.
Titulo: Design and Fabrication of a Novel Electrode-Supported Honeycomb SOFC
